<paragraph blockId="7.[136,1452,1348,1519]" pageId="7" pageNumber="198">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,462,1456,1482]" pageId="7" pageNumber="198">Habitat and ecology:—</emphasis>
The new species grows in secondary broad-leaved evergreen sparse forests at an elevation of 
<quantity box="[166,237,1492,1519]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.0" pageId="7" pageNumber="198" unit="m" value="700.0">700 m</quantity>
as a lithophytic herb on cliffs composed of eroded sandstone on steep slopes.
